<meta name="description" content="山形県最南端にある米沢市の公式ホームページです。暮らしの情報、防災、観光、移住、子育て支援、各種手続きなど、市民と来訪者に役立つ情報を掲載しています。ごみの捨て方や市民バスの情報も掲載しています。
Yonezawa City is located at the southernmost tip of Yamagata Prefecture. This is the city’s official website, providing useful information for residents and visitors, including daily life services, disaster preparedness, tourism, relocation, child-rearing support, and various administrative procedures.It also includes information on how to dispose of garbage and details about the city bus.">    <meta property="og:title" content="市公式トップページ|米沢市">
